{ 14.dxe5  is also a decent move, but I think the text does better at limiting Black's counterplay. }
14... Ndxe5
{ This is a standard sacrifice, but because dxe5 comes with tempo, it just doesn't work here. }
15. dxe5 d4 16. Bd2
{ I think keeping the diagonal closed is simplest, but taking on d4 is also good. }
16... Nxe5 17. Bxb4 Qxb4 18. Re1 Nxf3 19. gxf3
{ Black does not have enough play for the piece. } *

