{ ...cxd4 may be a genuine concern now that White lacks the Ne5 and Qa4+ idea. }
13... Bxc5 14. O-O Rc8 15. Qe2
{ White still holds some advantage. The Queenside majority is still present, and expansion on that side of the board is likely to factor into White's plans at some point. }
