{ This is an extremely rare move, which David Miedema, in The Modernized French Defense - Volume 2 considers to be promising. }
8. O-O cxd4 9. Re1+ Be7 10. Nxd4 Nc6 11. N2f3
{ A sensible arrangement of the Knights; d4 is well under control and Ne5 may become a tempting possibility at some stage. }
