{ With  Bxf6  in the air, Black should play the slightly strange looking  14...Bc7  , when White can choose between either  15.Bxf6  Qxf6  16.Bd5  , or a slower move such as  15.h3  . Black is very close to equal but it seems to me that he's under a bit of pressure. }
