Nb3 Nc6 9. Nbxd4 Nxd4 10. Nxd4 a6 11. Re1 Qc7 12. Bd3
{ This seems like an interesting move to me. As opposed to  12.Bb3  , White points the Bishop towards the Black Kingside. As opposed to  12.Qe2  , White leaves open the option of bringing the Queen to  f3  . It is also Leela's highest scoring choice. }
